OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780488668
OL,3,CRiot police clash with protesters in
OL,4,CSouthampton
OL,6,FITV News Correspondent Neil Connery
OL,7,Freports live from the scene
OL,9,FPolice holding riot shields have
OL,10,Fclashed with protesters close to where
OL,11,FHenry Nowak was stabbed to death.
OL,13,FDozens of police, along with the
OL,14,Fpolice helicopter, riot vans and other
OL,15,Femergency services are currently
OL,16,Fdealing with a large protest in the
OL,17,FPortswood area.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
