PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780488668
OL,3,CRiot police clash with protesters in
OL,4,CSouthampton
OL,6,FHundreds of people are still in
OL,7,Fattendance, having started their
OL,8,Fdemonstration in the centre of
OL,9,FSouthampton earlier.
OL,11,FTommy Robinson has also been in
OL,12,Fattendance at the protests, which
OL,13,Fbegan shortly before 6pm.
OL,15,FOfficers were pelted with stones on a
OL,16,Fresidential street in the St Denys
OL,17,Farea of Southampton before they
OL,18,Fcharged with perspex shields in an
OL,19,Fattempt to push the crowd back.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780488668
OL,3,CRiot police clash with protesters in
OL,4,CSouthampton
OL,6,FHowever, the crowds have pushed back.
OL,7,FSouthampton's local paper, the Daily
OL,8,FEcho, has also reported that
OL,9,Fprotesters are setting commercial bins
OL,10,Fon fire and rolling them towards
OL,11,Fofficers.
OL,13,FThroughout the evening, demonstrators
OL,14,Fcould be heard chanting "Henry,
OL,15,FHenry", as the line of police were
OL,16,Fpelted with bricks.
