OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780488668
OL,3,CRiot police clash with protesters in
OL,4,CSouthampton
OL,6,FChairs, cans and flares were also
OL,7,Fthrown at police in riot gear,
OL,8,Feventually forcing officers and three
OL,9,Fpolice vans back from the line they
OL,10,Fhad been holding in another area in
OL,11,FPortswood.
OL,13,FLocal community groups are appealing
OL,14,Ffor calm said they have recieved
OL,15,Freports of harassment towards Sikhs
OL,16,Fand Muslims.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
