OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780488668
OL,3,CRiot police clash with protesters in
OL,4,CSouthampton
OL,6,FOne told ITV Meridian: "There have
OL,7,Fbeen isolated reports from the
OL,8,Fcommunity of minor incidents of
OL,9,Fharassment towards Sikhs and Muslims
OL,10,Fbecause of the sad incident involving
OL,11,FHenry Nowak.
OL,13,F"His family have stressed the
OL,14,Fimportance of community cohesion and
OL,15,Fcalm.
OL,17,F"Please remain vigilant and if you
OL,18,Fexperience, hear or see any raciist
OL,19,Fbehaviour it is important to report
OL,20,Fit."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
