PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780488668
OL,3,CRiot police clash with protesters in
OL,4,CSouthampton
OL,6,FThe footage was made public after
OL,7,FVickrum Digwa, 23, was jailed for life
OL,8,Ffor murdering the 18-year-old
OL,9,FUniversity of Southampton student with
OL,10,Fa Sikh ceremonial knife.
OL,12,FSpeaking outside court after the
OL,13,Fverdict on Monday, Mr Nowak's father
OL,14,FMark had said that his family wanted
OL,15,Fto use Henry's story "to make change
OL,16,Ffor the better" rather than as fuel
OL,17,Ffor conflict.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
