OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780488668
OL,3,CRiot police clash with protesters in
OL,4,CSouthampton
OL,6,F"We do not want his death to be used
OL,7,Fto create further division, hatred or
OL,8,Ftension. We want his story to help
OL,9,Fmake our streets safer for everyone,"
OL,10,Fhe said.
OL,12,FThat plea was reiterated by the Home
OL,13,FSecretary Shabana Mahmood on Tuesday
OL,14,Fafter Reform UK leader Nigel Farage
OL,15,Fissued a statement about the case.
OL,17,FShe reacted to Tuesday night's protest
OL,18,Fwith a post on X, calling the scenes
OL,19,F"unacceptable" and saying: "There can
OL,20,Fbe no justification for hijacking this
OL,21,Ftragedy to stir up."
